<a href="http://drupal.org/project/image" title="http://drupal.org/project/image">http://drupal.org/project/image</a></p>
<p>TinyMCE<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/tinymce" title="http://drupal.org/project/tinymce">http://drupal.org/project/tinymce</a></p>
<p>Lightbox (well, Lightbox2)<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/lightbox2" title="http://drupal.org/project/lightbox2">http://drupal.org/project/lightbox2</a></p>
<p>Shadowbox<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/shadowbox" title="http://drupal.org/project/shadowbox">http://drupal.org/project/shadowbox</a></p>
