<a id="comment-31"></a>
<div class="comment odd"><div class="comment-inner">

      <h3 class="title"><a href="from-2500-ten-a-beginners-guide-module-selection#comment-31" class="active">Recommended modules etc. mentioned in session</a></h3>
  
  
  
  <div class="submitted">
    Submitted by <a href="tasha-caswell" title="View user profile.">tasha.caswell</a> on May 24, 2008 - 7:19pm.  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Well implemented, generic, customizable theme:<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/zen" title="http://drupal.org/project/zen">http://drupal.org/project/zen</a></p>
<p>Simple menu:<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/simplemenu" title="http://drupal.org/project/simplemenu">http://drupal.org/project/simplemenu</a></p>
<p>Update status (part of 6 core--will be prompted to update in admin):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/update_status" title="http://drupal.org/project/update_status">http://drupal.org/project/update_status</a></p>
<p>Pathauto (gives nodes more sensible paths):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/pathauto" title="http://drupal.org/project/pathauto">http://drupal.org/project/pathauto</a></p>
<p>Bad behavior (reduces # of script kiddies):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/badbehavior" title="http://drupal.org/project/badbehavior">http://drupal.org/project/badbehavior</a></p>
<p>Contact/Webform (can add extra fields; data shows up in tables in Webform admin; does stats):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/webform" title="http://drupal.org/project/webform">http://drupal.org/project/webform</a></p>
<p>Captcha (use w/ forms):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/captcha" title="http://drupal.org/project/captcha">http://drupal.org/project/captcha</a></p>
<p>Simple news (users subscribe/unsubscribe from mailing lists on their own; can upload existing mailing lists):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/simplenews" title="http://drupal.org/project/simplenews">http://drupal.org/project/simplenews</a></p>
<p>Content Construction Kit (CCK) (allows you to add arbitrary fields to nodes):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/cck" title="http://drupal.org/project/cck">http://drupal.org/project/cck</a></p>
<p>Imagefield name (name photos according to function and treat them different in Theme layer):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/imagefield" title="http://drupal.org/project/imagefield">http://drupal.org/project/imagefield</a></p>
<p>Imagecache (resizes image to fit theme):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/imagecache" title="http://drupal.org/project/imagecache">http://drupal.org/project/imagecache</a></p>
<p>Automatic node titles (create title for node from other elements of node):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/auto_nodetitle" title="http://drupal.org/project/auto_nodetitle">http://drupal.org/project/auto_nodetitle</a></p>
<p>Faceted search/CCK facets<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/faceted_search" title="http://drupal.org/project/faceted_search">http://drupal.org/project/faceted_search</a><br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/cck_facets" title="http://drupal.org/project/cck_facets">http://drupal.org/project/cck_facets</a></p>
<p>Views (List of [nodes, node teasers, one CCK field from many]; filter list in relevant way):<br />
<a href="http://drupal.org/project/views" title="http://drupal.org/project/views">http://drupal.org/project/views</a></p>
  </div>

  
</div></div> <!-- /comment-inner, /comment -->
